race.description: Lees Orchard Tassie Gold Apple Ht2 Standing Pace
race.comment: HEZA PUNK ROCKER NZ (5) has drawn wide in recent runs. Was outstanding last time out when successful by 1.5 metres over 2240m at Melton. Meets some better types this time but he has the ability to test this field. TRIEDTOTELLYA (10) resumes from a spell of five months after closing off last campaign in good form, scoring at his last appearance over 2090m at Hobart. Generally comes to hand very quickly, with four wins from five first-up appearances. Sure to be right there at the finish. RAGING WHITEBAIT NZ (1) was out of the money two runs ago then broke and finished fifth last start over 1720m at Melton, coming home 12 metres from the winner. Finds a nice race and can make up for that last start mishap. STEPPING STONES (9) must be respected after scoring last start by 1.5 metres at Hobart over 1609m.
